---------------------------------------------------------- WIFI Adaptor setup ----------------------------------------------------

# connect your wifi adaptor with the Virtual Machine

# once adaptor appeared on the VMware path ">> VM >> Removable Device >> Realtek 802.1 N" in the connected devices

>> lsusb

# then select the driver name at the end of the apaptor description (link: realtek-rtl8188eus)

>> apt install -y realtek-rtl8188eus-dkms

>> sudo shutdown -r now

--------------------------------------------------------------- ENJOY --------------------------------------------------------------
